[
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"413824\">Gary Guo</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/Module.2Fdriver-scoped.20data/near/572202149\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Support self-referential structs with pin-init, so you can reference a field from another</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>That is already possible in initializers. If you want a <code>'self</code>lifetime, more work is needed though</p>",
        "id": 572204779,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770310946
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This is indeed about lifetime, so we can use it as proof that the value is always initialized and skip runtime checks</p>",
        "id": 572205031,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1770311009
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We could have a <code>SelfRef&lt;T&gt;</code> smartpointer that's used by <code>init!</code> as the type for the references to existing fields (it implements <code>Deref</code>)</p>",
        "id": 572219907,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770315493
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I don't think it could implement <code>Deref</code>. It needs to return something that references &amp;'self and you cannot do it with <code>Deref</code>, which doesn't use GAT</p>",
        "id": 572220079,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1770315549
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>we need more stuff to support <code>'self</code> yes, but it can definitely implement Deref for convenience</p>",
        "id": 572220331,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770315629
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>How so?</p>",
        "id": 572220402,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1770315649
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>What's going to be the type for <code>Target</code>?</p>",
        "id": 572220592,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1770315714
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>T</code></p>",
        "id": 572220630,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770315723
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>8 messages were moved here from <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"288089\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/288089-General/topic/Module.2Fdriver-scoped.20data/with/572202149\">#General &gt; Module/driver-scoped data</a> by <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span>.</p>",
        "id": 572220686,
        "sender_full_name": "Notification Bot",
        "timestamp": 1770315741
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But lifetime would be wrong? How would I hold the reference to other field?</p>",
        "id": 572220918,
        "sender_full_name": "Gary Guo",
        "timestamp": 1770315818
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm not sure I understand.</p>\n<p>We can have this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SelfReferetial</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">64</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">// this ensures that we cannot move out of this field</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">buf_ptr</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SelfRef</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">64</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 572225598,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770317386
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">pin_init</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">SelfReferential</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">64</span><span class=\"p\">],</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">buf_ptr</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">buf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 572225701,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1770317419
    },
    {
